                                    <div id="elementor-tab-content-2561" class="elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix elementor-active" data-tab="1" role="region" aria-labelledby="elementor-tab-title-2561" style="display: block;">
                                       <p>M.F.M Digital Nepal is a project initiated by Nepalese youth with the aim of empowering fellow youth to become digitally savvy and harness the benefits of digitization to achieve financial freedom. We provide resources, guidance, and support to enhance digital literacy and financial knowledge.</p>
